Hi all,

Here is a small info about Kubernetes(K8s)

K8s is a container Optimization tool using for automating software deployment, scaling and management. 
In K8s, we have Pods.

Pod is a Kubernetes object. It consists one or multiple containers are created by kubernetes. we create the pods, Pods will create the containers.

###Few Commands###

1. kubectl get pod
2. kubectel get pod -o wide
3. kubectl get ns
4. kubectl get configmap
5. kubectl get configmap -n ns
6. kubectl get deployment dep.name
7. kubectl get services
8. kubectl describe nodes node name
9. kubectl describe pod pod name

Thank you..
